| Componente | Versión | Propósito |
|-----------|---------|----------|
| **Java** | 17 LTS | Runtime JVM |
| **Spring Boot** | 3.3.13 | Framework principal |
| **Spring Cloud** | 2023.0.6 | Service discovery, config |
| **Spring Data JPA** | 3.3.13 | ORM/Persistencia |
| **Spring Web** | 3.3.13 | REST APIs |
| **Spring OpenFeign** | Cloud | Comunicación inter-servicios |
| **MySQL** | 8.0 | RDBMS principal |
| **MySQL Connector/J** | 8.3.0 | Driver JDBC |
| **Flyway** | 9.22.3 | Migraciones de BD |
| **Lombok** | 1.18.46 | Boilerplate reduction |
| **Validation API** | 2.0 | Bean Validation |
| **Docker** | 3.8+ | Containerización |
| **Maven** | 3.8+ | Build automation |

